	<text_base_description>Extraordinary Celebrity Home with City to Ocean and Canyon Views. Nestled at the top of Hollywood Hills, this private and secluded home boasts 3576 square feet with an additional 600 square feet artist studio or home theater. Centrally located and just minutes away from Sunset Boulevard, enjoy stunning 360-degree views from downtown to Catalina and beyond. This is truly California living at its best. This property features a fluid indoor, outdoor loft-like open floor plan connecting the formal and family rooms with a fireplace, plenty of amazing natural light and easy access to the deck and pool. This sleek architectural design includes an inspired kitchen with dining area and recently updated beautiful hardwood floors throughout. Unwind in the master suite with balcony overlooking Los Angeles plus remodeled master bathroom with twin shower and a two-person spa tub. Step outside to relax, enjoy the waterfall pool and spa or sunbathe on the large deck with its sweeping city views.  </text_base_description>
